[0m[49m[39m  164, 168[0m:[39m[49m ### Ingredients
[0m[49m[39m  165, 169[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  166, 170[0m:[39m[49m | AWS Service | Role |
[0m[49m[39m  167, 171[0m:[39m[49m |------------|------|
